# Team Notes App - Design & Implementation Plan

I'll build a full-stack team notes application. Here's a complete, working implementation using React + Node.js/Express + SQLite (easy to run, no external DB setup needed).

## Features
- Create/edit/delete notes with rich text
- Organize notes into folders/workspaces
- Real-time-ish collaboration indicator (who's viewing)
- Tags and search
- Comments on notes
- User authentication (simple JWT-based)

