# Pomodoro Timer App

A complete, self-contained Pomodoro timer using plain HTML, CSS, and JavaScript — no external dependencies needed for this use case (a single-page interactive UI doesn't require frameworks or build tools).

## Features
- Configurable work/short break/long break durations
- Configurable number of work sessions before a long break
- Start / Pause / Resume / Reset controls
- Visual alerts (color change + pulsing animation + browser notification + sound beep) when a session ends
- Responsive layout (works on mobile and desktop)
- Progress ring showing time remaining visually
- Session counter

